summary: Adds a cosy, small cottage just south of Rorikstead
descriptionHtml:
Want a small, quiet cottage near Rorikstead? This cottage is equipt with everything an adventurer like yourself could need - a bed, a place to make and improve armour and weapons and a chest to store your items and a pot to cook at. And it\'s in walking distance of an inn! :D

Installation: Simply extract the .esp file to your Skyrim data folder.

My \"Cure Disease\" spell mod:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8269
author: Elderman357
